 <sect1 id="sec.user.instances.basics">
  <title>Introduction</title>
  <para>Instances are virtual machines that run inside the cloud. When launching 
  an instance, you select a virtual machine image that a cloud administrator
	has uploaded to &cloud;. You also need to specify the <quote>size</quote> of the
	VM to start (called <literal>flavor</literal> in &ostack; and to provide
	an SSH key.</para>
 </sect1>
